data.description: MLS# 271601 Welcome to your dream farmhouse-inspired home nestled in the heart of a highly sought-after neighborhood, where timeless charm meets modern comfort. Situated on  spacious corner lot, this residence boasts all the features you desire for a comfortable and stylish lifestyle. Step inside to discover an open-concept living space flooded with natural light. The gathering room features a cozy fireplace, perfect for coming together with loved ones on chilly evenings. High ceilings and large windows!! just a stone's throw away from top-rated schools, making the morning school run a breeze. Additionally, all your daily necessities, from shopping to dining, are conveniently located nearby, making this neighborhood truly desirable. This farmhouse-inspired gem offers a perfect blend of classic elegance and tasteful touches, making it the ideal place to call home. Don't miss the opportunity to make this corner-lot beauty your very own! Complete new HVAC as of 04/2023 & New Dishwasher. Assumable 5.875% FHA LOAN! 1 year home warranty through Old Republic
